==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: shēng bù dài lái, sĭ bù dài qù
===Etymology===
Literally: You can't bring it with you from before birth, and you can't take with you after you're dead.
===Proverb===
'''[[生]][[不]][[帶]][[來]]，[[死]][[不]][[帶]][[去]]'''
# used to advise people to refrain from being obsessed with material possessions
===Alternate forms===
[[生不带来，死不带去]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
